=E2=80=9D and she types =E2=80=9Cbuy 1 million shares of XYZ=E2=80=9D into =
her system, and the system sends that order to some third-party market make=
r who actually does the trade.</li></ol><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">You do=
n=E2=80=99t see a ton of this at the high end, because if you are an instit=
utional investor you probably care less about the snazziness of your broker=
