ith implications for struggling banks and brokerages around the world.</p><=
p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The goal is to offer such firms a white-label t=
rading service: They would deal with customers while Citadel Securities man=
ages the guts of their trading desks, including technology, analytics and o=
rder execution.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The nascent plan, described=
