</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bill Hwang was charged with market man=
ipulation because his family office, Archegos Capital Management, bought a =
ton of shares of about a dozen stocks, as sloppily as possible, with the ef=
fect and apparent intention of making those stocks go up. Yesterday <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/36027023.195406/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjQtMDctMTAvYmlsbC1od2FuZy1m=
b3VuZC1ndWlsdHktYWZ0ZXItdHJpYWwtb3Zlci0yMDIxLWFyY2hlZ29zLWNvbGxhcHNlP2NtcGl=
kPUJCRDA3MTEyNF9NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbG=
V0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTI0MDcxMSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b85=
24a319a23cBa80c3629" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=
=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; bord=
er-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: so=
lid; background-color: #ccc;">a jury convicted him</a>.<a class=3D"footnote=
-index" href=3D"#footnote-4" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none=
 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; d=
isplay: inline-block;">
<span>[4]</span>
</a>=C2=A0After the trial, it seems reasonably clear that Hwang wanted to b=
uy a ton of those stocks to push their prices up, and he told his trader to=
 do so. He wasn=E2=80=99t=C2=A0<em>just=C2=A0</em>buying lots of those stoc=
ks because he liked them, with the accidental side effect of pushing up the=
 prices; he really wanted to push up the prices, and bought in an aggressiv=
e manner to achieve that goal.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And th=
at=E2=80=99s probably illegal: Buying a ton of stock with the <em>intention=
 </em>of pushing up the price is market manipulation; it=E2=80=99s causing =
the price of the stock to reflect something other than real supply and dema=
nd.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-5" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none !important; background-color: tr=
ansparent !important; display: inline-block;">
