ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
Facebook Inc.</a>=C2=A0and <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.c=
om/click/36027023.195406/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydG=
ljbGVzLzIwMTktMDUtMTQvdGhlcmUtd2FzLW5vLXdheS10by13aW4td2l0aC10aGUtdWJlci1pc=
G8_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDcxMTI0X01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNl=
